that makes one forget pain.

00:03:15.629 --> 00:03:16.990
Be it pain

00:03:17.189 --> 00:03:18.629
or joy,

00:03:19.337 --> 00:03:22.099
they are trials given by Heaven.

00:03:22.100 --> 00:03:23.781
But I can't bear to see her suffer.

00:03:24.909 --> 00:03:26.069
I'd rather

00:03:26.550 --> 00:03:28.269
