00:03:28.270 --> 00:03:29.710
Have you ever considered this?

00:03:30.270 --> 00:03:31.949
What you call forgetting

00:03:32.230 --> 00:03:35.069
is taking away her life.

00:03:35.189 --> 00:03:37.750
I just don't want her to hate me.

00:03:37.830 --> 00:03:39.789
In one's life,

00:03:40.029 --> 00:03:41.795
joy, sorrow, reunion, and parting

00:03:42.069 --> 00:03:44.430
are all bound by fate.

00:03:44.710 --> 00:03:47.270
To forcefully erase her memories

00:03:47.390 --> 00:03:50.470
is to sever her karmic ties.

00:03:51.189 --> 00:03:52.629
Please, Your Reverence.

00:03:58.469 --> 00:04:01.549
This medicine will erase all her pain.

00:04:01.550 --> 00:04:02.829
