00:04:14.349 --> 00:04:16.949
Heaven?

00:04:17.230 --> 00:04:18.870
The law of cause and effect

00:04:19.150 --> 00:04:20.628
will bring its retribution.

00:04:20.629 --> 00:04:22.269
